Package: casemix
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Quality Measurement Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Denis Agniel
Maintainer: Denis Agniel <dagniel@rand.org>
Description: This package provides tools to use machine learning and causal inference techniques to estimate the quality of many units (or equivalently the causal effect of many treatments). It also allows the incorporation of equity concerns, where measurement is done in a population of observations that satisfy certain equity considerations.
